These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, apricot, onion, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, card-games, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, sailing, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##8
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person eating lettuce##6
 5. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person eating apricot##8
 8. the person eating apricot is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 9. the person eating pineapple is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
10. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
12. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4
13. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | pineapple         | lettuce     | onion     | apricot         |
| Hobby   | puzzles | collecting    | card-games     | chess |
| Sport   | cricket       | rowing | skateboarding | sailing       |

