.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, fanta, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, project-manager, architect, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, swimming, volleyball, climbing
 1. the architect is not to the right of the coach##8
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the project-manager##1
 5. the journalist is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta          | juice      | sprite      | 7up   |
| Job        | architect     | journalist | project-manager | coach      |
| Sport      | climbing | swimming    | parkour  | volleyball |

