.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, fishing, collecting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, funk, house
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, car, snowmobile
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not the fan of dubstep##6
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the fan of house##8
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing  | woodworking | collecting | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | dubstep      | house | funk        |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car       | snowmobile    | bus     |

