.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, drama, superhero, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, gospel, soul, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, american, british
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 2. the egyptian is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 3. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the egyptian##8
 6. the american is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 7. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
 8. the british is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 9. the nigerian is on the left of the american##1
10. the person watching action movies is the american##1
11. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | action | drama    | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | gospel     | trance   | r&b     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | american   | egyptian | british    |

