.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, drawing, filmmaking, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, thriller, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking       | rock-climbing | drawing  | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller       | crime    | adventure | drama    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | tennis   | volleyball   | cricket |

