.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, kiwi, banana, cucumber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, drama, family
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, japanese, spanish
 1. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 2. the person watching family movies is not the thai##6
 3. the japanese is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person watching family movies##7
 4. the thai is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 6. the japanese is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 7. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the spanish is between the person eating lemon and the japanese##2
 9. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
10. the person eating banana is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8
11. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | kiwi      | banana      | cucumber | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | time-travel    | family | spy     |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | japanese | spanish  | thai |

