There 4 different types of food: banana, grapes, watermelon, corn
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, techno, reggae, funk
1. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
2. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person eating watermelon##7
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the person eating banana is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
7. the person eating corn is the fan of techno##1
8. the person eating corn is somewhere between the fan of funk and the person drinking lemonade##7
9. the person eating corn is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | 7up | tea  | water |
| Food          | grapes | corn   | banana | watermelon |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | techno   | funk      | reggae      |

