.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, video-games, sudoku, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, argentine, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, roller, bike
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 2. the russian is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the argentine##7
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 4. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the colombian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 7. the russian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 8. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
10. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
11. the colombian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
13. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
14. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku | singing | video-games    |
| Nationality   | argentine  | russian    | colombian      | egyptian |
| Transport     | boat | scooter          | bike      | roller       |

