 4. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 6. the person watching satire movies is the lawyer##1
 7. the teacher is not to the right of the lawyer##8
 8. the lawyer is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 9. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
11. the paramedic is not the person drinking cola##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
