 4. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
 5. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
10. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
