The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, rowing, badminton
1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the pakistani is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
3. the person who's sport is badminton is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
4. the australian is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the pakistani is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the mexican##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is tennis##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the person who's sport is rowing is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | australian     | mexican  | nigerian |
| Pet           | hamster      | guinea-pig        | cat   | mouse |
| Sport         | tennis  | rowing | badminton | soccer       |

 